# ============================================
# API KEY SECURITY
# ============================================

# IMPORTANT:
# - Never commit .env.local to git (already in .gitignore)
# - Rotate API keys quarterly
# - Set spending limits in API dashboards
# - Monitor usage for anomalies
# - Don't share API keys in Slack/email

# For CI/CD:
# - Use GitHub Secrets for GitHub Actions
# - Use Vercel Env Vars for deployments
# - Use encrypted secrets management

